args: So this is your local cuisine, eh?\nPretty good chowâ€”we don't really\nhave flavors like this in Hinomoto.
I'm glad you like it. This is actually\none of my favorite places to take people.
Halp! Haaaaalp! My village is being\nattacked by fiends!
I got away but everyone else is still there!\nI need a mercenary or a soldier or a\nconstable or something pleeeeease!
I'll help ya out, girly...if ya gots the coin\nwhat to pay me for my trouble.
I'll give you everything I have!\nPlease just help them!
Right then! We got ourselves a deal.\nWhere this town'a yours at?
Just beyond the mountain over there.
Cor, but that's a long way off!

Considerin' how long it took ya to get
here, yer village is already worm's food.
Ain't no need for me to hustle all the way
there to find that out.
Th-that's not true! I know they're alive!
Nah, best that ya move on with yer life.\nWhat say you'n me forget about all this\nbusiness and go get somethin' to eat?
Unhand me, sir! I have to help my father\nand the rest of my village!
Show me the way to your village. \nI'll save 'em.
Hmph! Looks like some clown's tryin' to\nhorn in on my payday.
Yer a fool to go there! That place is dead,\nand ya damn well know it!
I don't care about the opinion of a coward.
When someone needs help, you help.\nThat's just the way of it.
Things are worse here than I thought.
These fiends are struttin' around like they\nown the damn joint, and there's not a sign\nof any people left...
Still, that ain't no call for me to\nsheathe my sword. HAAAH!
Heh. That? Just a scratch, is all.\nI'm only gettin' warmed up.
That terrible man was right.\nThis IS hopeless...
There's no one here.\nThe fiends have clearly...
Please, you must stop fighting now.\nThere's no need for more people to die.
'Scuse me? Are you seriously sayin' that?
I told you. I'm gonna save your people.
I'm a samurai. I don't break my word.
And if I ain't givin' up, you can't either!
Right then. Let's take these fiends down!
My blade is swift as the wind, fiends...\nand you'll meet your end on its edge!
Oh my gosh! You did it!
...Ow. Mighta pushed it a little there.
I may be shaking, but we did it.\nNow we can take our time and\nsearch for the townspeop...
Wait, do you hear that? It's more fiends!
We heard it get quiet and came out of\nhiding to see what happened.
Hiding in the mayor's basement along\nwith the rest of the villagers.
More importantly, what happened here?\nWho killed all these fiends?
It was these two men right here!\nWe owe them both our liv...
...Are you really okay with\nsneaking away like this?
If we'd stuck around, she woulda tried\nto pay usâ€”then the whole village\nwoulda tried to empty its coffers.
They'll need that coin to rebuild, and tryin'\nto turn them down woulda been a hassle.
You impress me more and more, Addis.
Eh, ain't nothin'. Oh, and sorry for draggin'\nyou along on my unpaid volunteerism.
Don't apologize. I wanted to help.
In that case, it's much appreciated.
